cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SY

The paper discusses the expressive power of recurrent neural networks, which is a topic related to machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also mentions the use of convolutional networks and image processing, which suggests a possible connection to computer vision (cs.CV). The use of tensor decompositions and numerical evidence of expressivity suggest a possible connection to numerical analysis (cs.NA) or systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper discusses the theoretical aspects of deep neural networks, which could also be related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
